    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 text-indigo-700 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-8">
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-pulse"></span>
      +500 ahorradores ya lo usan
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-[1.05]">
      Deja de regalar dinero<br class="hidden sm:block"> en suscripciones olvidadas.
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Trackea, gestiona y optimiza tus gastos recurrentes en 5 minutos. Recibe alertas antes de cada renovación y cancela lo que no usas.
    </p>

    <% unless user_signed_in? %>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <%= link_to "Get Started →", new_user_registration_path,
            class: "inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-base font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-700 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-150" %>
        <%= link_to "Ver precios", "#pricing",
            class: "inline-flex items-center px-6 py-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 transition" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-3 max-w-sm sm:max-w-md mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center px-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">$240+</span>
        <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1">ahorro promedio/año</span>
      </div>
